th:medium; border-left-color:black;\">-2.2\n</td>\n<td>9\n</td>\n<td>0.48\n</td>\n<td>1.35\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Leather Scout Gauntlets.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/74/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/74/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/74/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Gauntlets.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Leather_Scout_Gauntlets\"></span>Leather Scout Gauntlets<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">802</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>35</td>\n<td>8\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">1</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">-0.2\n</td>\n<td>19\n</td>\n<td>0.91\n</td>\n<td>2.19\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Leather Scout Helmet.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f5/SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Leather_Scout_Helmet.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Leather_Scout_Helmet\"></span>Leather Scout Helmet<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=